{"tid":763012,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"邊度話香港被剔除聯合國殖民地名單？","createTime":"2018-07-31T18:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T13:57:18.000Z","uid":130019,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f64dd5af0eff143b9e1213502e9755f8c8e78c28","tid":763012,"uid":130019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:31:38.000Z","msg":"背景資料：<br />\n二戰後，聯合國大會准許殖民地國家及民族獨立的自決權利。<br />\n1972年，根據英國國會, 維基等等既資料來源，<strong>聯合國大會第2908號決議</strong>決定香港不屬於殖民地。（簡單講，二戰之後，如果係殖民地就可以自決。詳細可睇維基<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E8%87%AA%E6%B1%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%258F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B1%25BA&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6df1d9c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E8%87%AA%E6%B1%BA</a>）<br />\n因為香港不再係殖民地，所以就冇左自決權。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果真係睇下呢份第2908號決議<br />\n英文版：<br />\nIMPLEMENTATION OF THE DECLARATION ON THE GRANTING OF INDEPENDENCE TO COLONIAL COUNTRIES AND PEOPLES<br />\n<a href=\"https://documents-dds-ny.un.org/doc/RESOLUTION/GEN/NR0/269/38/IMG/NR026938.pdf?OpenElement\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocuments-dds-ny.un.org%2Fdoc%2FRESOLUTION%2FGEN%2FNR0%2F269%2F38%2FIMG%2FNR026938.pdf%3FOpenElement&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=dfa571f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://documents-dds-ny.un.org/doc/RESOLUTION/GEN/NR0/269/38/IMG/NR026938.pdf?OpenElement</a><br />\n簡體中文版：<br />\n給予殖民地國家和人民獨立宣言的執行<br />\n<a href=\"https://documents-dds-ny.un.org/doc/RESOLUTION/GEN/NR0/267/91/IMG/NR026791.pdf?OpenElement\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocuments-dds-ny.un.org%2Fdoc%2FRESOLUTION%2FGEN%2FNR0%2F267%2F91%2FIMG%2FNR026791.pdf%3FOpenElement&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=adb58122\" target=\"_blank\">https://documents-dds-ny.un.org/doc/RESOLUTION/GEN/NR0/267/91/IMG/NR026791.pdf?OpenElement</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實一個字都冇講過香港<br />\n內文主要講點樣加快自決進程</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以我唔明白香港邊度被剔除聯合國殖民地名單？<br />\n如果係第2908號決議，咁邊部分講香港被剔走？<br />\n如果唔係，咁係邊份文件？<br />\n如果上面兩條問題冇答案，咁香港其實係唔係應該在聯合國殖民地名單？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該各位巴絲幫下手搵答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：純學術討論<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n英國國會議員問政府官員關於香港事務<br />\n政府官：... in <strong>Resolution 2908</strong> (XXVII) of 2nd November 1972 of a recommendation by the Special Committee on the Implementation of the Declaration on the Granting of Independence to Colonial Countries and Peoples <strong>that Hong Kong should be removed from the list of territories to which that declaration</strong> applies...<br />\n<a href=\"https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/written-answers/1976/dec/14/hong-kong-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.parliament.uk%2Fhistoric-hansard%2Fwritten-answers%2F1976%2Fdec%2F14%2Fhong-kong-1&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c3ed8477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/written-answers/1976/dec/14/hong-kong-1</a><br />\n<br />\nps 黃之鋒同敖卓軒曾經寫過關於呢個問題，但都解答唔到。不過都值得睇<br />\n黃之鋒、敖卓軒：港澳不算殖民地？1972年聯合國決議的真相<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20161102-opinion-joshuawong-jeffreyngo-hongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20161102-opinion-joshuawong-jeffreyngo-hongkong%2F&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2f51635b\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20161102-opinion-joshuawong-jeffreyngo-hongkong/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港民族主義#自決權<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9#%E8%87%AA%E6%B1%BA%E6%AC%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%258F%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25BE%25A9%23%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=dde46418\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9#%E8%87%AA%E6%B1%BA%E6%AC%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n聯合國大會第2908號決議投票紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"http://unbisnet.un.org:8080/ipac20/ipac.jsp?session=1371J646K5S55.209490&amp;menu=search&amp;aspect=power&amp;npp=50&amp;ipp=20&amp;spp=20&amp;profile=voting&amp;ri=&amp;index=.VM&amp;term=2908%28XXVII%29&amp;matchopt=0%7C0&amp;oper=AND&amp;aspect=power&amp;index=.VW&amp;term=&amp;matchopt=0%7C0&amp;oper=AND&amp;index=.AD&amp;term=&amp;matchopt=0%7C0&amp;oper=AND&amp;index=BIB&amp;term=&amp;matchopt=0%7C0&amp;ultype=PD01&amp;uloper=%3D&amp;ullimit=1972&amp;ultype=&amp;uloper=%3D&amp;ullimit=&amp;sort=&amp;x=17&amp;y=7#focus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funbisnet.un.org%3A8080%2Fipac20%2Fipac.jsp%3Fsession%3D1371J646K5S55.209490%26menu%3Dsearch%26aspect%3Dpower%26npp%3D50%26ipp%3D20%26spp%3D20%26profile%3Dvoting%26ri%3D%26index%3D.VM%26term%3D2908%2528XXVII%2529%26matchopt%3D0%257C0%26oper%3DAND%26aspect%3Dpower%26index%3D.VW%26term%3D%26matchopt%3D0%257C0%26oper%3DAND%26index%3D.AD%26term%3D%26matchopt%3D0%257C0%26oper%3DAND%26index%3DBIB%26term%3D%26matchopt%3D0%257C0%26ultype%3DPD01%26uloper%3D%253D%26ullimit%3D1972%26ultype%3D%26uloper%3D%253D%26ullimit%3D%26sort%3D%26x%3D17%26y%3D7%23focus&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=082fe18c\" target=\"_blank\">http://unbisnet.un.org:8080/ipac20/ipac.jsp?session=1371J646K5S55.209490&amp;menu=search&amp;aspect=power&amp;npp=50&amp;ipp=20&amp;spp=20&amp;profile=voting&amp;ri=&amp;index=.VM&amp;term=2908%28XXVII%29&amp;matchopt=0%7C0&amp;oper=AND&amp;aspect=power&amp;index=.VW&amp;term=&amp;matchopt=0%7C0&amp;oper=AND&amp;index=.AD&amp;term=&amp;matchopt=0%7C0&amp;oper=AND&amp;index=BIB&amp;term=&amp;matchopt=0%7C0&amp;ultype=PD01&amp;uloper=%3D&amp;ullimit=1972&amp;ultype=&amp;uloper=%3D&amp;ullimit=&amp;sort=&amp;x=17&amp;y=7#focus</a>"},{"pid":"dfe0e4af807e748787697ab5fd84d0436eb141a9","tid":763012,"uid":186661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T21:23:40.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"e6c3f70ef791e354392ef031774547ab6f6eafa3","tid":763012,"uid":165773,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:30:13.000Z","msg":"如果大陸都會講法律<br />\n5毛都會講道理。。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25ba3108e13c87205ea4a496e5867ce352e7e19","tid":763012,"uid":8984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:52:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/092pV3OvDwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F092pV3OvDwA&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0b19541b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/092pV3OvDwA</a><br />\n5:04 有講到"},{"pid":"2f23abf5ea0c687d6922e69470ebd2ef1bdff99b","tid":763012,"uid":125027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:59:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/decolonization/nonselfgov.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fdecolonization%2Fnonselfgov.shtml&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=066eaed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.un.org/en/decolonization/nonselfgov.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n有一行係Hong Kong - Change in Status - 1972"},{"pid":"3564d36fb9e411a94dead8e4ea6e407a8a950c4d","tid":763012,"uid":130019,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6c3f70ef791e354392ef031774547ab6f6eafa3","tid":763012,"uid":165773,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:30:13.000Z","msg":"如果大陸都會講法律<br />\n5毛都會講道理。。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:00:35.000Z","msg":"但今次有聯合國份喎<br />\n點都有牙力過英國"},{"pid":"e6b23c445c6e36ae9ab466402f3a3c73e7469617","tid":763012,"uid":155732,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3564d36fb9e411a94dead8e4ea6e407a8a950c4d","tid":763012,"uid":130019,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6c3f70ef791e354392ef031774547ab6f6eafa3","tid":763012,"uid":165773,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:30:13.000Z","msg":"如果大陸都會講法律<br />\n5毛都會講道理。。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:00:35.000Z","msg":"但今次有聯合國份喎<br />\n點都有牙力過英國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:02:43.000Z","msg":"聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有撚用咩<br />\n點解會踢走台灣呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b112078bb7c7c356ac8c7329a26de45b8cf5b9f6","tid":763012,"uid":130019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f23abf5ea0c687d6922e69470ebd2ef1bdff99b","tid":763012,"uid":125027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:59:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/decolonization/nonselfgov.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fdecolonization%2Fnonselfgov.shtml&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=066eaed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.un.org/en/decolonization/nonselfgov.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n有一行係Hong Kong - Change in Status - 1972"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"我搵到既每一個source 都係指第1908號決議(1972)剔除左香港出殖民地，所以就係change in status<br />\n<br />\n但真係咬文嚼字咁睇份決議<br />\n都冇冇講過關於香港<br />\n（至少我搵唔到 如果有巴打搵到 唔該同我講)"},{"pid":"accd4c9427952d0e8b22667685f07c28683c20bb","tid":763012,"uid":130019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b112078bb7c7c356ac8c7329a26de45b8cf5b9f6","tid":763012,"uid":130019,"like"