8%3D&h=fc8c5237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.xuite.net/hoonting/twblog/160091366-UN%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E7%AC%AC2908%E8%99%9F%E6%B1%BA%E8%AD%B0%EF%BC%881972%E5%B9%B411%E6%9C%882%E6%97%A5%EF%BC%89</a><br />\n<br />\n不過的確有official document 係寫明左remove 左due to China request:<br />\n<a href=\"http://legal.un.org/repertory/art73/english/rep_supp5_vol4_art73.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flegal.un.org%2Frepertory%2Fart73%2Fenglish%2Frep_supp5_vol4_art73.pdf&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemooviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7d593383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://legal.un.org/repertory/art73/english/rep_supp5_vol4_art73.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"事緣中國入到聯合國之後就寫左封信講香港同澳門唔係殖民地<br />\n係中國領土不過俾英葡佔領左<br />\n<br />\n咁中國講完都要有人認同先得<br />\n認同份文件應該就係2908 <br />\n但我睇2908又冇喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:47:50.000Z","msg":"睇番佢article 73份野係話<br />\nThe General Assembly, by its resolution 2908 (XXVII), approved the report of the Special Committee on decolonization that included the recommendation regarding the two Territories.<br />\n所以可能要搵番果份report先會有details，佢個網好似搵唔倒1972既report。<br />\n<br />\n然後睇到annex 2又會發現其實GA冇&quot;considered&quot;過就remove左。<br />\n<br />\n所以我戴住頭盔咁估個special committee 覺得中國齊clues claim番香港就落左report，2908又有提到legitimacy，好有可能係成份report一次連D African countries 一齊vote過左，而70年代個個都想fing甩D colonies + reject 就violate 左value，對於西方中國又冇而家咁大威脅，所以pass左真係好正常。戴住頭盔咁講。"},{"pid":"a200bb76b3cd15403b80fc682759461088d7c40f","tid":763012,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:13:09.000Z","msg":"宜家係中國殖民地"},{"pid":"f486f27844c69fd9975d38f062d4696e70e249d7","tid":763012,"uid":130019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a200bb76b3cd15403b80fc682759461088d7c40f","tid":763012,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:13:09.000Z","msg":"宜家係中國殖民地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"如果成功講得番香港理應係殖民地個l